              <Value type="System.String, mscorlib, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089">
                <string>Hi There,

The Dispatch Note Export from Sage 200 failed for Abode Shop, please check that the maximum number of users for Sage 200 has 
been reached.

If you still receive this error after rectifying the above, please send an email to paul@instantcart.com or call 0113 256 0200 for further assistance.

Many Thanks

Zynk
P.S: I Reside on the Sage 200 server under the Windows user "Sync", I will retry to run the workflow 3 times every 10 minutes after this message has been issued.</string>
              </Value>
